Object: Ball - This is a small bouncy ball which emits a trail of light 

Fields:

float x - determines the position of the ball.
float y
boolean facingUp - determines the direction which the ball is facing
boolean isSmall - determines the size of the ball
boolean emitTrail - emits the light trail from the ball

Methods:

bounce()
moveUp()
moveDown()
moveLeft()
moveRight
